The '''Annals of Aman''' are the second chapter of ''[[Morgoth's Ring]]'', the tenth volume of ''[[The History of Middle-earth]]''. It consists of detailed chronology from the creation of the world through the end of the [[First Age]], including an explanation of time reckoning in [[Valian Years]].

